Package: nifti.io
Type: Package
Title: Read and Write NIFTI-1 Files
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Timothy R. Koscik [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Timothy R. Koscik <timkoscik+nifti.io@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Description: A set of tools for reading and writing NIFTI-1 files. Unique operations include voxelwise read/write operations and a simplified method to write table contents to NIFTI_1 files. While compressed files cannot be used, memory requirements and read/write speed are optimized.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
